OL,3,CFamily business 'heartbroken' after
OL,4,Cfairy trail doors stolen
OL,6,FA family business in Guernsey says it
OL,7,Fis "incredibly saddened" after three
OL,8,Fhandcrafted fairy doors were stolen
OL,9,Ffrom its free children's trail.
OL,11,FBruce Russell and Son are a fifth
OL,12,Fgeneration jewellers near the island's
OL,13,Fairport in St Saviour and have put on
OL,14,Fthe summer hunt in their gardens.
OL,16,FHowever, within weeks, the business
OL,17,Fsays some of the markers have been
OL,18,Ftaken.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
