FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1783711191
OL,3,CFamily business 'heartbroken' after
OL,4,Cfairy trail doors stolen
OL,6,FThe post continues: "We really hope
OL,7,Fthe missing doors are returned.
OL,8,FUnfortunately, if they aren't, or if
OL,9,Fany more doors are stolen or damaged,
OL,10,Fwe may have no choice but to remove
OL,11,Fthe doors altogether.
OL,13,F"If you have taken one of the doors
OL,14,Ffor any reason, we kindly ask that you
OL,15,Fplease consider returning it. No
OL,16,Fquestions asked."
OL,18,FThe community has reacted with shock
OL,19,Fand disappointment, while one child
OL,20,Fhas already offered to create
OL,21,Freplacement fairy doors.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/3
